						               													<description>This is a simple roll and move game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During set-up, each player takes a coloured playing piece and four teddy weather cards, each depicting a teddy bear dressed for different weather (snowy, windy, sunny, and rainy weather).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a player's turn, the active player selects one teddy weather card and they then spin the weather spinner. If the weather selected by the spinner matches the teddy weather card chosen by the player, then the player can roll the dice and move that many spots on the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If a player lands on a storm cloud space they must return to the start.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player to reach the honey pot at the centre of the board wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
